item.text: Max has a good sense of what needs to be collectively done but maybe unsure how to get it done. Max is working both short and long term goals.
Max sees himself as a citizen of the world more than a faithful employee. He appreciates that money gets things done and contributes generously from his own middle-class income.
Max is more likely to point to a couple of startling statistics for shock effect than try to explain the meaning of large complex systems.
Max uses federated wiki as his personal blog. He will used a visualization to find and catalog contradictions but isn't likely to assemble a new visualization himself.

Max depends on reader metrics to tune his messages for maximum impact. This popular top-ten lists are sometimes tuned for outrage. This leads to more statistics which he happily quote. (All publicity is good publicity.)
